{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"610241-andhare-kino-koy","title":"আন্ধাৰে কিনো কয়","description":"আমাৰ অনুভৱবোৰ নো আচলতে কি? মৰমৰ যদি গোন্ধ থাকিলহেতেঁন তেন্তে কেনেকুৱানো গোন্ধালেহেতেঁন? যাদু বোলা কথাটোনো কি? এইয়া হৈছে দৈনন্দিন পৃথিৱীৰ সৰু সৰু ঘটনাবোৰত এভুমুকি। সিবোৰক এবাৰ ওচৰৰ পৰা চোৱা, কাণ উনাই কথাবোৰ শুনা আৰু প্ৰতিটো বস্তুৰে সৌন্দৰ্যক উদযাপন কৰা।","language":"Assamese","langCode":"as","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Dr. Khammoun Phukan"],"illustrators":["Krishna Bala Shenoi"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Pratham Books","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/610241-andhare-kino-koy"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/727644/size3/ffa8aee73935162cd6a249a70158794e.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/727644/size6/ffa8aee73935162cd6a249a70158794e.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/626138/size6/105a797c7ad6e48ff14a120cf2dd19a9.jpg","text":"আন্ধাৰে কিনো কয় মোৰ জানিবলৈ বৰ মন যায়।\nসেয়ে এদিনাখন ৰাতি মই তাকেই শুনিবলৈ বাহিৰলৈ ওলালো।","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/626139/size6/b1fde0b8ec3b21811281959bed282bdf.jpg","text":"3/18","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/626140/size6/14dc40654cb1a62591938dd70fbcba38.jpg","text":"কুকুৰ এটাই ভুকি আছিল।\nতাৰ বাহিৰে\nচৌপাশে\nকেৱল\nনীৰৱতা।","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/626144/size6/f27a4bdd2ed18cc90ef62239a9ca11aa.jpg","text":"বিস্ময় নো কি এবাৰ অনুভৱ কৰিবলৈ মন গ’ল।","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/626146/size6/347e19fbbf1f9a0aebca2b13961da400.jpg","text":"গতিকে মই বিশাল গছ এজোপা চুই চালো।","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/626149/size6/6b0687956ac6734d9cccb492c36a0f9d.jpg","text":"গছজোপাৰ গা-গছডাল বৰ খহটা আৰু টান, পিছে দুহাতেৰে আঁকোৱালি ধৰিবলৈ\nবৰ ভাল।","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/626151/size6/bd499fcc49992ec331da5ebf70eb4d93.jpg","text":"আৰু এদিন মৰমৰ গোন্ধনো কেনেকুৱা মোৰ জানিবলৈ মন গ’ল।","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/626153/size6/23bd82378ee21e3d270c2f60fcc8a3a9.jpg","text":"পিছে সেই কামটো তেনেই সহজ।","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/626155/size6/2474febbe30385a5787a207d9799bbf2.jpg","text":"মোৰ চিধাই কে’কলৈ\nমনত পৰিল!\n(আৰু এই কে’ক বনোৱা আইতাজনীলৈ।)","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/626142/size6/eb65ad1aee9c97f258b66e6330776886.jpg","text":"এই যে খেলিমেলি হোৱা, তাৰ নো সোৱাদ কেনেকুৱা তাকো জানিবলৈ মন গ’ল।","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/626145/size6/1067d2a0d7abd2147c14d548091c4239.jpg","text":"12/18","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/626148/size6/edcb175a490eed8658a500bb2fc3aa89.jpg","text":"গতিকে মই এটা সপোন চোবাই গিলি পেলালো।\nতাৰ সোৱাদ মচমচীয়া, অলপ টেঙা-মিঠা আৰু অলপ লিকতীয়া —\nমোৰ যে ভালদৰে মনত আছে।","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/626150/size6/607a8e6e134266e9aff17d4e6de2bc37.jpg","text":"এদিন আকৌ যাদু নো কি মোৰ জানিবলৈ মন গ’ল।\nসেইবাবে মই ওপৰৰ আকাশৰ ডাৱৰ এথোপালৈ চাই পঠিয়ালো।","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/626152/size6/78ab7067171c7ac04d96471a7278e944.jpg","text":"15/18","words":null},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/626154/size6/fdd79d26c6135e9d35e8afb375aae055.jpg","text":"আৰু তলত জমা হৈ থকা পানীৰ খুবলিটোলৈ।","words":null},{"n":16,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/626156/size6/9a06bd2c9d131cadacf0d7a7515f17f9.jpg","text":"17/18","words":null},{"n":17,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/626157/size6/8ce7b6d717b372e1551bfba77e50c8ee.jpg","text":"বাহ! মোৰ আশে-পাশে দেখোন যাদুয়েই যাদু।","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":17,"words":143}}